ivardefs.name: category_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies what kind of team.  This is to support differentiation between multiple co-existing teams, such as care plan team, episode of care team, longitudinal care team.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifiers assigned to this care team by the performer or other systems which remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

ivardefs.name: managingOrganization_
ivardefs.desc: The organization responsible for the care team.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A label for human use intended to distinguish like teams.  E.g. the "red" vs. "green" trauma teams.

ivardefs.name: participant_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies all people and organizations who are expected to be involved in the care team.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: Indicates when the team did (or is intended to) come into effect and end.

ivardefs.name: reasonCode_
ivardefs.desc: Describes why the care team exists.

ivardefs.name: reasonReference_
ivardefs.desc: Condition(s) that this care team addresses.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the current state of the care team.

ivardefs.name: subject
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the patient or group whose intended care is handled by the team.

ivardefs.name: telecom_
ivardefs.desc: A central contact detail for the care team (that applies to all members).

properties.desc: The Care Team includes all the people and organizations who plan to participate in the coordination and delivery of care.
